These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, security-guard, accountant, scientist
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, amaryllis, lily, marigold
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, tea, sprite
1. the person who growsamaryllis is the fan of techno##1
2. the person who growslily is between the accountant and the scientist##2
3. the person who growsamaryllis is the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the person drinking tea is the accountant##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the scientist##1
8. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
9. the security-guard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Job   | security-guard | scientist   | software-developer  | accountant  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Flower   | marigold | amaryllis | lily | bellflower |
| Beverage     | sprite  | milk       | hot-chocolate    | tea     |

