.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, tower, ranch-style
4 different games are played: billiard, domino, whist, scrabble
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, russian, thai, canadian
1. the canadian is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the russian##1
4. the tower house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
5. the person playing scrabble is between the owner of the frog and the turkish##2
6. the canadian is between the person playing scrabble and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person playing domino is on the left of the tower house##1
9. the person playing whist is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| House         | ranch-style | cape-cod    | tower  | farmhouse    |
| Game   | billiard      | domino  | scrabble  | whist |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Nationality         | russian    | canadian | thai | turkish |

