.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, dutch, canadian, argentine
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, lilac, azure, red
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, crime, action, sports
1. the person who likes azure is the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who likes red##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the canadian is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who likes lilac is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the argentine is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the indonesian is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the canadian and the person who likes lilac##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Nationality        | dutch | canadian     | indonesian   | argentine     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| Color         | turquise   | azure | red       | lilac    |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | crime | fantasy  | sports    |

