.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, cain, davidoff, montecristo
City: rome, prague, paris, berlin
House: cape-cod, colonial, futuristic, modern
