 2. the montecristo-smoker is the fisherman##1
 3. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the modern house##1
 4. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
 5. the montecristo-smoker is the person traveling to prague##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 7. the cain-smoker is the police-officer##1
 8. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the colonial house##1
10. the mechanic is between the person traveling to rome and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Cigar   | montecristo | bolivar  | davidoff | cain       |
| City           | prague       | berlin    | paris      | rome           |
| House         | cape-cod | colonial   | modern   | futuristic         |

