 3. the security-guard is the fan of techno##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the mexican is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 6. the fan of rock is on the left of the mexican##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the fan of disco##1
 8. the lawyer is the argentine##1
 9. the fan of rock is between the person playing whist and the egyptian##2
10. the chinese is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Music-Genre          | techno         | rock         | disco     | d&b      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
