3. the polish is between the ritmeester-smoker and the dutch##2
4. the owner of the snake is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
8. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
9. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
