The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
House: townhouse, cottage, gothic-revival, futuristic
There 4 different types of food: lime, apricot, watermelon, blueberry
 1. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is the gothic-revival house##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the gothic-revival house and the person eating watermelon##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person eating blueberry##1
 5. the futuristic house is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 7. the townhouse house is the person eating lime##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
10. the gothic-revival house is the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower   | iris | daffodil | sunflower  | balloon-flower  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| House   | townhouse   | gothic-revival   | futuristic | cottage |
